commentaries.text:
وقوله تعالى: { لَّجَعَلْنَا لِمَن يَكْفُرُ بِٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ لِبُيُوتِهِمْ سُقُفاً مِّن فِضَّةٍ وَمَعَارِجَ عَلَيْهَا يَظْهَرُونَ }
 والمعَارجُ: هي الدَّرجُ
 ويَظهَرونَ: معناه يَعلُونَ ويَصعَدُونَ

translations.translation:
And the saying of Allah, {We have made for those who disbelieve in the Merciful houses of silver, and [for] them are stairs [of silver] by which they ascend}


And the ma'arij are the degrees (of ascent or descent).


They show themselves {off}, meaning they act arrogant and superior.
